    <title type="html"><![CDATA[去掉“是否要关闭本窗口”的提示]]></title>
    <link href="http://NeoCN.github.com/blog/2009/07/19/window-close-with-no-prompt/"/>
    <updated>2009-07-19T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://NeoCN.github.com/blog/2009/07/19/window-close-with-no-prompt</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>想要在javascript里调用window.close(); 关且闭窗口时不提示“是否要关闭本窗口？”有以下两种方法可以实现这样的效果：</p>




<p>方法一、</p>




<p><pre lang="javascript">
window.opener = null;
window.close();
</pre></p>




<p>方法二、</p>




<p><pre lang="javascript">
window.opener = window;
window.self.close();
</pre></p>

]]></content>
